metadata.description: S.H.I.E.L.D. as you know it may be gone, and that's bad news for Earth and Nick Fury! There's a new danger stalking Nick; to stop it, he must band with trusted allies inclduing Alphonso "Mac" Mackenzie, and the alluring Contessa Valentina Allegra de la Fontaine!
metadata.name: Nick Fury, Agent of S.H.I.E.L.D.
